  <brief_title>A Phase 3 Study of Rilotumumab (AMG 102) With Cisplatin and Capecitabine (CX) as First-line Therapy in Gastric Cancer</brief_title>
  <acronym>RILOMET-2</acronym>
  <official_title>A Phase 3, Multicenter, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo Controlled Study of Rilotumumab (AMG 102) With Cisplatin and Capecitabine (CX) as First-line Therapy in Advanced MET-Positive Gastric or Gastroesophageal Junction Adenocarcinoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
