  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a Phase 3, multicenter, randomized, double-blind, placebo controlled study of
      Rilotumumab (AMG 102) with Cisplatin and Capecitabine (CX) for untreated advanced mesenchymal
      epithelial transition factor (MET)-positive gastric or gastroesophageal junction
      adenocarcinoma (GEJ).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Terminated</overall_status>
